            "x1": 119,
            "y1": 182,
            "x2": 1711,
            "y2": 315
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 4,
        "text": "कीन्ह प्रणाम जोरि युग पानी । दीन अशीष राम सुखमानी ॥",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/dudhadasa1900_08_textline_4.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 114,
            "y1": 280,
            "x2": 1718,
            "y2": 404
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 5,
        "text": "बहुरि जाय मातन शिर नावा । आशिषपाय परम सुखपावा ॥",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/dudhadasa1900_08_textline_5.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 111,
            "y1": 382,
            "x2": 1718,
            "y2": 498
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 6,
        "text": "पुनि सीता पद नायोशीशा । लह्योपरमसुख पाय अशीशा ॥",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/dudhadasa1900_08_textline_6.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 111,
            "y1": 470,
            "x2": 1718,
            "y2": 585
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 7,
        "text": "भोजन कीन्ह संग सब भाई । बैठे प्रभु सिंहासन जाई ॥",
